content: Some premier brands and retailers that expanded their operations with us by opening new online stores in new countries during the third quarter were: H&M, adding a store in Uruguay, currently operating in five countries in Latin America; Motorola, adding a store in Saudi Nation, currently operating in 19 countries across the world with more than 20 stores; and Whirlpool, adding a store in Germany, currently operating in 16 countries across the world with more than 30 stores.
